suggest_text_def:
1. Iswr-a jwngni gwgwm no,
Gilu baluao negra,
Biw dahalbw thungribw,
Jwngkhou basainw rwngou.
Gwjam bisarua
Bwrabgasinw dong
Orkhrebnw hasthaiyw
Binw bwlwgrathar;
Mansia bijwng haya.

2. Jwngha bwlwa gwithara,
Thabnw pejenjatharw,
Oblabw hasingwi nonga,
Jwngjwng lwgw lagra dong.
Nwng bikhou mithigou,
Biw Jisua-nw,
Daoha nangnaiphwrao,
Derhaphlaigra Jisu;
Swrgwni Phwrbuanw.

3. Switanphra jwngkhou homblabw
Bwrabnanwi orkhrebnw,
Jwngha ginangnai gwithara,
Jisu-a derhahwgwn.
Bwrabthwng switana,
Biha bwlw gwia,
Bisara jakhabai,
Phejengwn Jisu-a;
Phongselo bathrajwngnw.

4. Thagwn Iswr-ni bathraya,
Jeblabw jwbnai nonga,
Iswr-a jwngjwng lwgwse,
Gaoni Jiu ar bwlwjwng.
Mwdwmkhou butharbla;
Gotho-gothai, bihi,
Mankhwubw selangbla,
Ma mwndergwn biswr?
Swrgwa Jwngha thagwn.

1. Gwthar, Gwthar, Gwthar,
Bwlwgrasin Iswr,
Phungjaniao Nwngkhounw
Bakhnaitharw jwngw,
Gwthar gwthar gwthar
Onkhothar ar hagra,
Sathamjwng saselo
Iswr Nwngw.

2. Gwthar gwthar gwthar,
Swrgwniphra boibw,
Nwngkhou khulumnw
Jo jadwng Nwngni mwkhangao.
Kerubim ar Seraphim
Nwngniao gugrubdwng,
Dongmwn dabw dong Nwng
Ar thaphlaigwn.

3. Gwthar, gwthar, gwthar,
Nwngnw srangao dongo;
Phaphiphra Nwngni
Mohimakhou nunw mwna.
Gwtharanw Nwnglo
Ar raobw gwithara,
Nwng bwlwgra ongra
Ar mwjangthar.

4. Gwthar, gwthar, gwthar
Bwlwgrasin Iswr;
Nwngjwng Swrjijanaiphra
Nwngkhounw bakhnaithwng.
Gwthar, gwthar, gwthar
Onkhothar ar hagra
Sathamjwng saselo,
Iswr Nwngw.

1. Hayao thanai mansi mani,
Rongja bajaywi rwjabdwng.
Phwrbukhou ginanwi khulum,
Bikhou bakhnainanwi rongja.

2. Phwrbua nwngthargou Iswr,
Dongnai manikhou Swrjigra.
Jwng Phwrbu-ni, Biw khangw,
Biw gumnanwi nephlaiyw.

3. Baknaiwi baknaiwi habdw,
Rongja baja Bini noao.
Gwbarwi baknaibai thadw,
Phwrbuni gwthar mungkhounw.

4. Phwrbu Iswr-a gahamthar,
Bini onnaia jwbthara.
Bini bathraya gahamthar,
Gwdwniphrai ar jeblaibw.

5. Bipha, Bica ar Gwthar Jiu,
Boinibw gwthar Iswr-a,
Mansijwng ar arphophwrjwng,
Jwbajase baknaijathwng.

1. O Swrgwni gedert Iswr,
Lagarbw jwngw bakhnaiyw;
Hayaobw ar nokhrangaobw,
Nwnglonw dersinthar Iswr.

2. Santhro haywi arphophranw,
Nwngni mwkhangao gosongdwng;
Rwjabnai ar baknainaijwng,
Nwngkhounw khulum-phlaidwngw.

3. Gwthar, gwthar, gwthar Iswr,
Phwrbu nwngw bakhnaijathwng;
Gwjou nokhrang ar hayaobw,
Nwngni mohima bungphobdwng.

4. Nabiphwr ar swlwngraphwr,
Ar gaswi Nwngni sakkhiphwr;
Doyajwng gohwjanaiphra,
Nwngni mungkhounw baknaiyw.

1. Bwlwgrasin Iswr-khounw,
Da jwng baknaidwni,
Hajw gedert undwikhoubw;
Binw swrjijwbdwng.

2. Gwjou nokhrang dwi
gwthoubw,
Binw Swrjijwbdwng,
Bithai bibar manikhoubw;
Gaoni bwlwjwngnw.

3. Jwmwi jayw, barbw barw,
Bini bathrajwngnw,
Nokhrangniphrai dwijlang
horw;
Gaoni onnaijwngnw.

4. Gwbrab anjartniphrai Biw,
Jwngkhou basaiphlaiyw,
Phwrbu-khou jwng manw
baonw ?
Biw basaigrathar.

1. Boikhoubw dagra Bi,
Boikhoubw khanggra Bi,
Boikhoubw ongra Bi,
Bwlwgra Iswr Bi.

Gwsw hwswnanwi
Hanthu srong khoraidw,
Akhai khobjobnanwi
khulumdw;
Swrjigra Iswr-khounw.

2. Gaswinw gwswjwng,
Gaswinw bwlwjwng;
Gaswinw jiujwngnw,
Iswr-khou khulumdw.

3. Khathini mansikhou,
Gaokhou badi ondw;
Hephajab hwphlaidw,
Jobra jonthaphwrao.

1. Nwngni munga,
Nwngni mohimabw
Phwrbu Iswr,
Manijagra jathwng,
Jiu maniabw,
Mengnai lengphrabw,
Raigra mania;
Nwngninw mungkhou
Khwthagwn.

2. Nwng Iswr, jwng nunw
Mwnablabw,
Nwngnw Iswr
Boibw thwijwbblabw,
Phiriphra thangw,
Gaswi swlaiyw,
Swrgwniphrainw;
Iswr-a jwngnw
Hwphlaiyw.

3. No' gedertbw,
Ha' gaswibw jwbgwn,
Ha' ar nokhrangabw
Gwglwithargwn,
Hajw thikhinibw,
Thabnw gwmwrgwn,
Gwjwng san badi;
Iswr-ni raijwa
Phwigwn.

1. Iswr-anw dadwng, khangdwng,
Ondwng phederdwng.
Dasim sarijanai niphrai
Jwng boikhoubw.

De, thu jwngw
Khulumdwni gwswjwng
Phwrbu Iswr-khou.

2. Mwdwm jiunw
Nanggou phwrkhou
Biw hwphlaidwng.
Jahw-lwnghw phwjwnphlaidwng,
Jiu mwdwmkhou.

1. O angni jiu baknaidw
Gedert raojwng
Phwrbu-khounw,
Bini mungwi rongjadw
Hambai, hambai
Hwnnanwi nwng,
Nwngni phap'khou susrananwi,

Biw nwngkhou phengw
Biw nwngkhou linglangw,
Gaoni bamnaiaonw,
Biao jirainanwi nwng
Gwjwnw mengblabw.
Dhwrwmia Phwrbu-a,
Bwlw gwiywiphwrkhou
neyw.

2. Nonggouni bathrakhounw
Jwngnw nujahwbai Biw,
Gaoni Bica houajwng
Gwjwnnaikhou hayao
horbai,

Bini gedert onnaianw,
Sanaobw horaobw,
Gigraphwrkhou banjaiyw,
Bini gwjwnnaia
Gwswkhou rongjahwyw.
Gwthousinthar dwiao,
Gaoni doyajwng Biw,
Garbai angni phapmanikhou.

3. Bipha badinw Biw
Gaoni undwiphwrkhou onw,
Jwng maoriaphwrnw Bi
Gaokhou Bipha mungkho hwbai;

Phwtharni gangsw badi jwng
Dinwi mwjang bardwng,
Gabwn sirigwn thabnw
Barjwng maonai bilai,
Bibadinw jabai jwng,
Hayaonw thasandi
Bikhou mithinanwi bi,
Jwngkhou hephajab hwyw Bi.

4. Jwbtharajase thagwn
Bini gedert onnaialo,
Phiriniphrai phirisim
Gaoni saikhojanai phwrkhou
Phwrbu-a nephlaibai thagwn.

Bini gwsw badi
Mwjangwinw maonanwi
Onnaiao nwng thabla;
Swrgwao Biniaonw
Arphophwrjwng nwngnw
Rongjananwi rwjabgwn
Mohima mania Bini.

1. O Apha Nwngni
Gahamkhou bakhnaini,
Dan badi horbai
Jisu-khou be hayao.

Halleluya baknaijathwng
Nwngni mohima,
Halleluya phwjakhangdw
Jwngkhou O Phwrbu.

2. Jwng boibw Gwthar
Jiu-khounw baknaini,
Biw basaigrakhou
Jwngnw dinthibai.

3. Swdrimathar thwinai
Menda bicaya,
Golgathayao jwngni
Phap'khou banlangdwng.

4. Obla jwng boikhoubw
Phwthangdw Nwngw,
Boinibw gwswao
Onnaia jwngthwng.

1. Apha-ninw akhaiao
Bwlwmanianw dong.

Iswr-nw man hwnw thakhwi,
Lagarbw jwngw rongjani,
Jisu Kristo-ni mungwi.

2. Jisu-a jwngnw hwgwn
Jwbnai gwiywi gwthangkhou.

3. Gaoni sukh ar mohima
Biw jwngnwbw ranbai.

1. Hasthainai manikhounw,
Bikha khamnaikhoubw
Swrgwao thagraniao
Gwhwjwng gothaidw.
Biw barkhou thwnphlaiyw,
Okhabw hahwyw.
Nwng thangwn lamakhoubw
Biw mithikhagou.

2. Phwrbu-khou gwswkhangdw
Obla mwjang jagwn.
Bini maonaikhou naidw
Obla nwngbw maogwn.
Gabnai jinga sinaijwng,
Nwng isebw mwna;
Nwng mungbw lanw haya,
Iswr-anw hwyw.

3. O phwthaijagra Apha!
Nwnglo mithijwbgou
Angniao gahamkhounw.
Bikhou hasthaiyw Nwng.
Ar Nwng jekhou maojenw,
Bi japhung jwbthargwn.
Gaswibw gongnw nanggwn
Nwngni gwsw badi.

4. Switanni bwlwphranw
Daoha nangphwiblabw,
Nwng bikhou mungbw sana,
Biw mungbw nonga.
Nwng okha khwrwmhwbla
Swr gosongpthabaonw ?
Nwng onnanwi bwr hwbla
Swr sao hwnw hagou ?

5. Gabnaimanikhou gardw
Phwrbu-niao gothai,
Borsa khalam, O gwsw,
Gwhw khalamdw nwng!
Nwng bigba janw nanga,
Nwng thwnnw nanglia,
Iswr-a raja jathwng,
Mwjang maophlaiyw Biw.

1. Angkhounw nagarnanwi
Gubun Iswr gwia.
Jiu gwiywi muskhakhounw
Nwngswrw dakhulum.

Gaham Iswr Nwngni mung
Boijwngbw man hwjathwng !
Jwng phwthainanwi nwngkhou
Sanphrwmbw khulumgwn.

2. Nongkhai-bakhai dalathar,
Iswr-ni mungkhounw.
Gwthar sankhou gwswkhang,
Biao nwngswr jirai.

3. Nwma-nwmphakhou mani,
Mwjang gotho badi.
Raobw mansiphwrkhounw,
Nwngswrw dasithar.

4.Mungbw gajri habayao
Akhai dahwthar nwng.
Malaini mungaphwrkhou,
Nwngswr sikhao dakhao.

5. Nongkhai sakhi dagosong,
Nonggoukhoulo bungdw.
Malaini mungaphwrkhou,
Nwngswrw dalubwi.

6. Iswr-ni hukhumphwrkhou,
Angw gwswkhanggwn.
Onkho Phwrbu angnw hw,
Gwdan gwthar gwsw.

Bwr hwgra Iswr-khou baknai
Swrjijanaimani baknai.
Swrgwni daoha nanggraphwr,
Bakhnai Bipha, Bica, Jiukhou.

1. Nwngni munga dersin Iswr,
Doyajwngnw bungjase,
Sanphrwmbw jeraobw nuyw
Aglai biglai onswnai.
Sagwr, nwgwr, ha' ar nokhrang
Somainaywi Jwngblaodwng,
Swrjijanai manianw
Nwngni mankhou khwthayw.

2. Obla Jisu-niphwr, boibw,
jwngbw Bikhou bakhnaini,
Aglai biglai doyakhounw
Boinwbw Jwng khwthani.
Basaigraya dertsin raja,
Boibw Binw man hwdw.
Jisu-anw labwphadwng,
Swrgwkhou jwng boinwbw.

3. Gwswmanijwng rwjabdw,
Iswr-anw onnaikhai,
Man ar mohima lagarbw
Nwnninwkha O Iswr.
Jwbnai gwiywi gwthangkhounw
Swrgwao Jwng mwnthargwn,
Damkhou hwbai Nwng O Iswr
Jwngw makhou hwphinnw ?

1. Swrgwni Phwrbu
Iswr-khounw
Bakhnaibai thadw.
Bi jwngkhou dananwi bwrkhoubw
Hwgasinw dong.
Gedert raojwng,
Hambai hwnnanwi Bikhou
Lagarbw bakhnaibai thadw.

2. Ongra Phwrbu
Jisu Kristo-khou
Baknaibai thadw.
jwngkhou basainw
Swrgwniphrai
Hayao phwidwngmwn.
Basaigra Bi,
jwng gwmanaiphwrkhounw
Bikhounw phwthaini jwngw.

3. Jwngkhou gwthar
Khalamgra Jiu-khou
Baknaibai thadw.
Bilonw Swrgwni lamakhou
Jwngnw khwthayw.
Bini thwijwng,
Phapniphrai gokhayw Jwng,
Jwngnw gwjwnnaikhou hwgwn.

4. Sathamjwng saselo
Iswr-khou
Baknaibai thadw.
Biniaonw Jiukhou mwdwmkhoubw
Mwnkhabai Jwng.
Gwjousinni,
Apha arw basaigra
Nwngkhounw baknaiyw jwngw.

1. Lagarbw Nwng Jwngni hephajab hwgra
Swrjia sayaonw Nwngnw dongkhayw,
Swr bijirnw hagou, Nwngni mohima
Arw Nwngni Jwbnw gwiywi akholkhou ?

1. Hajarse bwswra Nwngha sanselo,
Mugaya Nwngnw be badinw Phwrbu,
Bobekhani Jwngninw jiuni sanphwra
Sanphrwmbw gwkhrwiywinw Jwblangdwngswi.

2. Barjwng biphang bilai siriyw badi,
Nwngni hukhumjwngnw, mansiphra thwiyw.
Jwngw Nwngni doyajwng gwthangwi dong
Nwng nongabla jwngw, boibw thwithargwn.

3. Nwngni bwrabnainiphrai bouha kharnw ?
Bouha thangnanwi Nwngniphrai kharkhmanw ?
Gangphwrjwng sagwraonw birlangblabw,
Biaobw Nwngni akhaiao gwglwiyw.

4. Mithigrakhai Nwng gaswibw mithigou,
Nwngniphrai raobw, kharkhmanw hathara;
Swr bijirnw hagou, Nwngni mohima
Arw Nwngni Jwbnw gwiywi akholkhou.

1. O lwgwphwr gwswkhangni
Iswr-anw jwngkhou dadwng,
Bini bathrakhou khwnasong
Khwnasongabla gedert phap.

2. Bini bwlwa gederthar
Nokhrang ar hakhou Swrjibai,
Junarphwrkhou,
Mansiphwrkhou
Gaswikhou Biw Swrjibai.

3. Bebadi Jwngkhou bungdwng Bi:
O boibw hani mansiphwr,
Phapmanini phrainw khardw
Angw phwiphina sayaonw.

4. Angni thingwi gwsw phindw
Phap'ni lamakhou gardw.
Angni bica Jisu-niao
Borsaywi hephajab ladw.

5. Gajri gwswkhou Binw hw
Biw nwngswrkhou susragwn,
Nwngswrw Bikhou khulumbla
Obla swrgwao sohwigwn.

1. Iswr-a onnai,
Basaibai Angkhou,
Iswr-a onnai,
Angni thakhwi.

Bikhainw rwjabw
Iswr-a onnai
Angkhou onbai.

2. Ang narsinjadwng,
Gilirt phap'jwngnw,
Ang narsinjadwng
Bi basaibai.

3. Basaigra Jisu
Basaibai Angkhou,
Basaigra Jisu
Bi Basaibai.

4. O ongra Iswr,
Basainai dwimu,
O ongra Iswr
Gwjwn hwgra.

5. Baknaiyw Nwngkhou,
Onphlaigra Iswr,
Rwjabgwn Nwngkhou
Jiu jwbjase.

1. Angni Iswr, jeblanw angw nuyw,
Swmw nangthao Nwngni maonaikhounw;
Hathorkhiphwr, okha khwrwmnaiphwrbw;
Nwngni swrjinaia bese gedert.

Angni jiua, Phwrbukhou bakhnaiw,
Angni Iswr, Nwngw gedert,
Angni jiua Phwrbukhou khulumw,
Iswr Nwngw bese gedert.

2. Jebla angw, hagrayao thabaibaiw,
Daosenphwrni rwjabnai khwnayw
Hajwniphrai, jebla ang naigonghorw,
Nijrani dwi gusu bar mwndangw.

3. Apha Iswr, gaoni bicakhou horbai,
Haya ang bujinw ma maya bi;
Phap'manikhounw, Biw Krus-ao banbai
Jiukhou hwbai, angni phap' susranw.

4. Gedert raojwng, jebla Kristo phwiphingwn,
Angkhou langnw, bese rongjagwn ang!
Biao gugrubnanwi khulumthargwn ang,
Mithihwgwn Phwrbu Nwng gederthar.

suggest_text_1: Bese gedert onnai O Iswr Apha-21
suggest_text_def:
1. Bese gedert onnai O Iswr Apha,
Unphina Nwng Nwngni onnainiphrai.
Feleng jaya, swlaia Nwngni onnai,
Jerwi dongmwn ar oraibw thagwn.

Bese gedert onnai
Nuyw ang phungphrwmbw gwdan onnai,
Angnw nangoumanikhou hwphlaiyw Nwng
Bese gedert onnai angni sayao.

2. dwijlang meseng horo, hanai bwthwrphwr.
San okhaphwr ar jwnglariphrabw;
Sakhi hwyw gaswi mithinggaya,
Nwngni gedert onnai ar maonaikhou.

3. Phap'phwrni nagarnai ar gwjwnnai hw,
Nwngni onnaijwng angkhou dwidendw;
Dinwini bwlw ar gabwnni mijingk,
Hajar bwswrphwrni bwr angnw hw.

1. Iswr gangkhong saikhlumao
Jirainw mwngwn.
Mwdwmni maonainiphrai,
Jiuni jingga sinaiao;
Iswr gangkhong saikhlumao
Jirainw mwngwn.

ou jirai, gwjwnwi ar rongja,
Iswr gangkhong saikhlumao.
ou jirai, gwjwnnai ar rongjanai,
Biaonw mwnnw hayw.

2. Iswr gangkhong saikhlumao
Bebadi gwjwn.
Bujinainibw bangsin,
Mablabw jwbthara;
Iswr gangkhong saikhlumao
Bebadi gwjwn.

3. Iswr gangkhong saikhlumao
Jwbwi rongjanai.
Rongjanaijwngnw bungdwng,
Gubunnwbw khwthadw;
Iswr gangkhong saikhlumao
Jwbwi gwjwnnai.

1. Somainaini Phwrbu Iswr,
Baknaiyw jwng rongjanan;
Geolang bibar badi Nwngkhou,

Khulumphlaigwn ang orai,
Phap' dukhuni khwmsi saikhong

Hwkharbai Nwng angniphrai,
Hwbai sanni srang badinw,
Usiglainai rongjanai.

2. Ha' ar nokhranga phwrmaiyw,
Nwngni akhaini haba;
Rwjabw Nwngni baknainai,
Hathorkhi ar arphophra.
Hajw-hayen, hagra-hama,
Phwilao dwima ar sagwr,
Daophwr ar bwhwinai nijra,
Lingw jwngkhou baknainw.

3. Nwng nagargra ar dan hwgra,
Orai bwrjwng Swphunggra;
Thangnan thanaini nijwra,
Gwjwnnainaini dwimu Nwng.
Nwngnw Bipha, anggw lwgw,
Onjlaigraphra Nwngninw,
Gaojwng gao onjlainw phwrwng,
Jiuni rongjanaiao dwn.

1. Iswrkhou bakhnaidw, Bi gaswi maobai!
Songsarkhou onnanwi Bisakhou horbai;
Phap'khou Biw banbai, jiukhoubw hwbai,
Boinwbw kheobai gwthangni dorkhou.

Iswrkhou bakhnaidw! Khwnasong Bini rao,
Iswrkhou baknaidw! Mansiphra rongjathwng,
Boibw Jisu-jwngnw Iswr-niao phwidw;
Baknaidw swrjigra Iswr-khounw.

2. Nwngthargou basainai, thwijwngnw bainai!
Iswr-ni bankhanai phwthaigraphwrnw;
Phapiblabw nwngw gwsw phwthaibla;
Oblanw Jisu-a khema hwgwn.

3. Mwjangthar phwrwngnai, gederthar maonai!
Jisu-Jwnglo Jwngw rongja phlaithargwn;
Jisu-ni mwkhangkhou Swrgwao nubla;
Gedert raojwng Bikhou bakhnaithargwn.

1. Iswr Nwngni doyayanw,
Bwr ar mwjangni thakhwi,
Dwijlang bwthwr jwngnw horw;
Bwswrphrwmbw gwdan bwr.
Swphungw gwsw bwlw,
Thaihwyw gwthang bithai.
Bwthwrkhou O gedert Iswr,
Onnaijwngnw Nwng
horphlaiyw.

2. Gedert gurwi Iswr Nwngw,
Onnaiabw jwbthara,
Phap'phwrkhou nagarnaijwngnw,
Gwdan Eden banaiyw.
Angkhounw onbai Nwngw,
Gwthar Jisu-ni mungjwng.
Angkhou gwtharphwrjwng sanpha,
Gwthang bwlw gaswiaobw.

Phwrbu Iswr ma esegrap'
Onhordwng Nwnglai angkhou.

1. Sarinainiphrai dinwisim,
Gedert gwlao phederbwdwng;
Ondwng khangdwng
Angkhou Nwngw,
Be hakhounw
Nuhwdwng Angkhou,
Nwngni onnaijwngnw.

2. Nwngni onnaia jwbthara,
Bwhwiphlaidwng dwimubadi;
Mwdwm jiunw
Nanggou phwrkhou,
Hwphlaidwng Nwng
Aglai biglainw,
Angw bia sayao.

1. Angkhou dwidendw O Phwrbu,
Gwjan lama be hagrao.
Ang udaiywi, Nwng bwlwgra;
Hompthadw Nwng akhaijwng.
Jiuni janai, jiuni janai,
Swrgwniphrai jwngnw hw.

2. Phwrbu angnw kheonan hwdw,
Jiuni gwthang dwimukhou.
Nwngni jiu gwjwn jwmwijwng;
Dwidenlangthwng sigangao.
Bwlwgrathar, bwlwgrathar,
Jiuninw Nwng dwidengra.

3. Jordan serjwng angw thangbla,
Angni ginaikhou hwkhar.
Thangbla hakhou garnanwi ang;
Swrgwao Nwng angkhou lang.
Rwjabnaijwng, rwjabnaijwng,
Baknaigwn ang lagarbw.

1. Bi dwidendwng gaham sannai!
Be bathrajwng ang gwjwnbai,
Ang jeraokhi thaya manw;
Iswr-a dwidenw Angkhou.
Bi dwidenw, bi dwidenw,
Gaoni akhaijwng dwidenw;
jagwn angw Bini sela,
Biw angninw dwidengra.

2. Borsa gwiywi thanangblabw,
Edenni sukh mwnablabw!
Som som dwi ar dwithunaobw;
Borsaywi thagwn Biniao.

10. Buhumao borsa gwithara lwgwphwr,
Swrgwni thakhwilo maodw lwgwphwr.

1. Iswr Apha dinwi jwngw,
Nwngniaonw aros gabw,
Onnaijwng Jwngkhou dwidendw,
Be gwdan bwswraobw Nwng.

2. Nwngni gangkhongni saikhlumao,
Jwngni mwdwm ar jiukhoubw,
Dwndw Nwngw gwjwnwinw;
Thani jwng Nwngni doya-yao.

3. Jwngni bengga khwmaphwrjwng,
Khwnasongnan lanw haya,
Nwngni gwthar bathra-phwrkhou,
Jwngnw Nwng hephajab hwdw.

4. Nwng doyani akhaijwngnw,
Dwidenlangdw Jwngkhou Nwngw,
Be gwdan bwswr jwbjase;
Nwngni doyakhou hwphlaidw.

5. Nwngkhou nagarnanwi jwngw,
Sohwinw haya Swrgwao,
Nwngni gwthangni dwijwngnw;
Nwngw Jwngkhou gwjwnhwdw.

1. Gwjam bwswr bargobai,
Phwrbu Jisu Jwngniao,
Nwngni gedert doyajwng,
Gahamwinw Jwngw dong.
Nwngni gangkhong saikhlumao,
Gwjwnnaikhou mwnw jwng.

2. Binikhainw Jisu jwng,
Santhro haywi baknaiyw,
Doyani khabukhoubw,
Arw gwdan bwrkhoubw;
jwng bia sayaonw Nwng,
Hwbai bephwr gaswikhou.

3. Jwngni phap'manikhoubw,
Nwngw onnanwi nagar,
Gwjam dai manikhounw,
Gaswikhou baojwbdw Nwng.
Sajani bodol onnai,
Arw gurwi gwsw hw.

1. Wi Apha Swrjigiri,
Baknaiyw jwng dinwi Nwngkhounw.
Sa-khwla, sanja-swnab,
Dwidenbwbai Nwngw jwngkhou
Jo khalambai.
Bikhainw Nwngni munga jwbajase
Hambai hwnjathwng...Apha Iswr.

2. Wi Apha Swrjigiri,
Hambai hwnw dinwi Nwngkhounw.
Baidisina anjartniphrai, labwbai Nwng
Thangnai bwthwrao.
Nangoumani hwjwbnanwi gotho-gothai,
Phwthangbwbai Nwng...Apha Iswr.

3. Wi Apha Swrjigiri,
Khulumw jwng dinwi Nwngkhounw.
Angkhalblabw jahwdwng Nwng,
Longthongblabw ganhwdwng Nwng
Thangnai bwswrao.
Ayo ! habap'ma maya,
Nwngni onnai maonai mania..
...Apha Iswr!

4. Wi Apha Swrjigiri,
Onnanwi Nwng bwr sarsrihort.
Jamba jambi, haoria phapi,
Phwidwng jwngw Nwngkhou khulumnw.
Onnaijwngnw hwdw jwngnw bwr ar bwlw
Nwngkhou khulumnw...Apha Iswr.

Wi hambai Iswr Nwngw Apha!
Bwthwr gwdanni phwjakhangdwng.

1. Khwlw-khwlw sudem bara bardwng,
Bilai Gwdanjwng bibar bardwng.

2. Daosen-daola honwi rwjabdwng,
Swlai-Swlo ayo bwthwralai.

3. Rindao-rindao sandung jwngblaodwng,
Biphang-laiphangjwng somaiphobdwng.

4. Iswr-ni bagana gwjwnhwyw,
Bini onnaia bese mwjang.

5. Iswr-a onnanwi khangw jwngkhou,
Gaoni bwlwjwng dwidenbwdwng.

Jisu-a onkhangbaobai,
Bini onnaikhou ang nubai,
Thaiywi biphangaonw jaonanwi hasar hwbai.

1. Bwswrtham bithai mwntharakhwiswi bigbaya,
Negrakhou danphainw thwnmaraswi.
Bini khaolainaibadi dwnthoaswi.

2. Hasar mwnnanwi bilai gwdanjwng bithai thai,
Phwsab jabaogwn nwng onjanaijwng.
Thaiabla rua honwi gudiao dong.

3. Nanggalao akhai homnanwi danaiphin nwngw,
Adri jagwn hayao, Jisu bungdwng.
Loth-ni hinjaoa naiphinnanwi thwidwng.

1. Iswr thangnai bwthwrphwrao,
Hephajab hwphlaigra,
Phwigwn bwthwrphwrao borsa,
Jwngni thaphlaigra no'

2. Nwngni singhason saikhlumao,
Gwtharphra thaphlaiyw,
Nwngni akhaia bwlwgra,
Ginw nangthara jwng.

3. Hajwphwrkhou daya sayao,
Jebw gwiya sayao,
Jajenwiniphrai Nwng Iswr!
Jwbajase thagwn.

4. Hajarse bwswrphra nwngha,
Thangkhanai san badi,
Horni phohorse badilo,
San ongkhara sayao.

5. Mugaya kharlangw badi,
jwng boibw langjayw,
Boibw simang badi jwbw,
Som jablanw thwiw.

6. Iswr thangnai bwthwrphwrao,
Hephajab hwphlaigra,
jwng gwthangwi thasandi ne,
jwng thaphlaigra no'ao.

1. Iswr Nwngw mansiphwrnw,
Gaoni bwrkhou hwphlaiyw.
Dwijwng maiphwr mwjang jayw,
Angkhoubw pheder bwrjwng,
Angkhoubw,
Angkhoubw pheder bwrjwng.

2. Iswr Apha, ang phapikhou,
Onnanwi danagarthar.
Mansiphwrnw hwyw badi,
Angnwbw bwr hwdw Nwng,
Angnwbw,
Angnwbw bwr hwdw Nwng.

3. Phwrbu angha bwlw gwiya,
Danw Nwngw bwlw hw.
Phapiphwrkhou Nwng linghorw,
Angkhoubw Nwng linghordw,
Angkhoubw,
Angkhoubw Nwng linghordw.

4. Dhwrwm jiukhou ang khananw,
Mwjangwinw nuhwdw.
Paul badi Jisu-nikhou,
Oraibw angnw phwrwng,
Angnwbw,
Oraibw angnw phwrwng.

5. Bipha, Bisa ar Gwthar Jiu,
Nwngni bwrjwng dwidenlang.
Mansiphwrkhou baikhobai Nwng,
Angkhoubw de baikhodw,
Angkhoubw,
Angkhoubw de baikhodw.

suggest_text_1: Phiri phiri bwthwra, Bere rungnai badi-92
suggest_text_def:
Phiri phiri bwthwra, Bere rungnai badi,
Runggolangw di buhumni bikhaniphrai.

1. Ala golaywinw bargolangjwbw bwthwra,
Nenw hathara raokhoubw mugaya.
Siri mwndw dinwi...
Be hani rongjanai, Gajri akholniphrai,
Hompthadw gaokhou gothaidw Phwrbu-niao.
Oblasw mwngwn nwng, Jwbrwngwi gwjwnnaikhou.

2. Siri siriywinw, khargolangjwbw bwthwra.
Sansohaya raobw Iswr-ni mohimakhou!
Andaihwgwn jwngkhou....
Phwrbu-niao thayabla gaswi holai jagwn,
Andailangjwbgwn switanni phakhonao.
Gwsw swlaidw de, Iswr-khou sibinaiao.

Gwdan bwswr sophwibai da,
Gwdan gwswjwng thabaidw.
Jisu-ni mungwi damnaiphwrjwng,
Derhanai nisan dikhangdw.

1. Sikhangdw boibw Kristan-phwr,
Gothai gaokhou Kristoniao.
Gaham Bathrakhou nwngswrw,
Gaswiaobw khwthabaihwi.

2. Nongkhai dhwrwm gwmwrlanggwn,
Inai mania jwblanggwn.
Phwrbu Jisu bungnai raoa,
Nongthargouwi japhungjwbgwn.

3. Gwdan srangninw jwngnaia,
Jisu-anw jwngni sranga.
Hwkharnanwi gaswi khwmsi,
Nujaphwibai bikhou phwthai.

Beseba somainai, Beseba rongjanai,
Dinwi jwngha halw-dwilw be somao.

1. Gwdan bwswrni gwdan sanao,
Barbwdwng ayo gwdan bara.
Phwjwnghordw Apha, mansini gwswao,
Bwrkhou sarsrihornanwi

2. Gwdan bwswrni gwdan gwsw,
Boibw lani jwng gwdan gwhw.
Daogalangni jwngw gaswi buhumao,
Phosongnw srangni raijw.

O Phwrbu Nwng onnanwi,
Jwngkhou gwthangwi nebwbai,
Thangnai bwswrniphrai nwibe bwswrsim.

1. Phwrbu Nwngni onnaia jwbnw gwithara,
Binikhainw jwngbw Nwngkhou baonw hathara.

2. Thangwi thangwi thangjwbbai gwjam bwswra,
Phwiwi phwiwi sophwilaibai gwdan bwswra.

3. Aros gabw jwng dinwi boibw Nwngniao,
Dwidenlangdw Nwngw jwngkhou nwi be bwswrao.

Dinwini dinalai bese somaina
Apha Iswr-ni onnaia bese gedert.

1. Dwidenbwbai Biw jwngkhou onnanwi,
Gaswibw nidanao basainanwi
Gwsw hwnanwi khulumni jwng
Bwlwgra Iswr Aphakhou.

2. Sa-khwla, sanja-swnab dwidenbwbai
Dinwini be gwdan bwswrsimao.
Deglaibw basaithargwn jwngkhou
Iswr-a gaoni doyajwng.

3. Angkhalblabw, nidanblabw sohai hwyw,
Iswr-a jwngkhounw rongjahwyw.
Hambai hwnnanwi khulumni jwng,
Onnanwi khanggra Aphakhou.

1. Nwng gaoni raj khwrthi,
Ar singhason garnan,
Be hayao phwidwngmwn Nwngw,
Bethlehemaonw
Jaigakhou mwnakhwiswi,
Nwng gwtharsinninw thakhwi.

Angni gwswao phwidw Phwrbu,
Jaiga dongo beaonw Nwngnw;
O Phwrbu Jisu
Phwithardw Nwng,
Jaiga dong beaonw Nwngnw.

2. Swrgwni arpho-phranw,
Nwngkhou rwjabdwng,
Nwngni mungkhou baknainanwi;
Nathai hayaonw
Haoriathar jananwi,
Sarijabai angni thakhwi.

3. Sialphwrha gudung dong,
Daophwrha baha,
Hagrani bongphang saikhlumao;
Iswr-ni bisajla gaoni,
Khoro dwnnw
Mwnakhwiswi jaigakhounw.

4. Gwthar bathra lanan Nwng
Phwidwngmwn Phwrbu,
Phapiphwrkhou basaitharnw;
Suni khwrtijwn omasi
Khalamnanwi,
Nwngkhou langbai
Golgathayao.

5. Jebla rwjabbaogwn,
Arpho-phra swrgwao,
Derhananwi Nwngw phwibai;
Bwi sanao angkhoubw,
Linghordw obla Nwng,
Jaiga dongo nwngnw hwnnanwi.

1. Nabijwng bungjanai,

Judaini Bethlehem
Nwgwraonw Biw,
Bininw munganw
Emmanuel.

2. Swrgwni sukh no'khou,
Nagarnanwi Biw,

Mansikhou onnanwi,
Gaonw nujaphwibai.
Mansiniao
Sarijaphwinanwi.

3. Sanja hadort-niphrainw,
Gwnwkhwphra ongkhardwng,
Hathorkhi gwdanni,
Nisankhounw lananwi.
Mwnbai biswr gaoswrni,
Sankhangnai badinw.
Gwdan rajayanw
Sarijabai.

4. Rongjaywi ongkharbai,
Jisu-khou naigirnw,
Judaini Jerusalem,
Herod rajaniao.
Sonhwibai rajaniao,
Biswr sohwinanwi,
Bi gwdan rajaya
Bouha dongo ?

5. Sasthwrao lirkhanai,
Mithinaikhai biswr,
Bethlehem nwgwraonw,
Ongkhar langphinaswi.
Hathorkhianw biswrkhou,
Dwidenlangphinbai,
Dolot thahwiaswi
Goli no'ao.

6. Rongjabai hathorkhi,
Thanaikhou nunanwi,
Hap'hwibai goli no'aonw,
Biswrw boibw,
Sona, rupha, gondoros,
Gaswikhou hwnanwi,
Khulumbaibw
Jisu rajakhounw.

1. Rongja songsar
Phwrbu phwibai,
Najao Bi rajakhou;
Binw jaiga tham thim khalam,
Rongjananwi boibw.
Rongja, rongjananwi boibw.

2. Rongja songsar

Rwjabnanwi baknai;
Hagra, hajw, dwima, onthai,
Baknaidw Bikhounw.
Baknai, baknaidw
bikhounw.

3. Phap'ar dukhu
Dajathwngswi,
Hayao su dathathwng;
Phwibai Bi bwr hwnw thakhwi,
Usiglaijasenw.
Usi, usiglaijasenw.

4. Raijw salainw gwthangwi,
Boibw hariphwrjwng;
Bini dhwrwm-ni akhola,
Swmw nangthao thao-thar.
Swmw, swmw nangthao-thaothar.

1. Rongja bajania,
Bwr ar basainaia,
Jisu Kristo-ni jwnwma,
Gwmadwng jwngw,
Jisu-a phwibai,
Rongjani, jwngw boibw.

2. Rongja bajania,

Jisu-ni sikhangphinnaia,
Khajadwng jwngw
Jisu-a kheobai,
Rongjani, jwngw boibw.

3. Rongja bajania,

Rongjani, jwngw boibw.

4. Rongja bajania,
Bwr ar basainaia,
Jisu-ni doyani maonai,
jwngkhou phap'niphrai,
Binw basaiw,
Rongjani, Jwnw boibw.

1. Phapi mansi phwrniaonw,
Jisu Kristo-a phwitharbai.
Bisaphwrkhou onnaikhainw,
Gaoni sukhkhou garnanwi.

2. Switanni phakhonaonw,
Biw jwngkhounw naihorbai,
Gonaini bwlw gwiyamwn,
jwng nwrkhwni bisamwn.

3. Switanni dudung phwrkhou,
Jisu-a thabnw hasobai,
Jwngw Bini thwinaijwngnw,
Switanniphrai gokhabai.

4. Biw jwngni bibankhou,
Onkhangnanwi gaonw banbai,
Switanni bwlwkhou Biw
Krus-aonw phwjwbtharbai.

5. Iswr-ni bwrabnaikhou,
Jisu-a phwjwbtharkhabai,
Biw swrgwni dorkhounw,
Jwngninw thakhwi kheobai.

6. O phapiphwr gwkhrwinw phwi,
Gapgra gwswjwng Biniao,
Switanphwrkhou nagarnanwi,
Jisu-niao kharbwdw.

7. Biw switanniphrainw,
jwng phapiphwrkhounw basaigwn,
Jwngkhou onnaikhai bwlwjwng,
Swrgwaonw langphagwn.

1. Khwnasong lwgwphwr,

Basaigra Jisu-a phwibai,
Gedert onnaijwng,

Phwthaigraphwr
Boikhoubw basaigwn.

2. Switan phwrniphrainw,
khartharni, khartharni,
Nwrkhwao khwkhlwigwn jwngkhou.
Githao bathao biswr,
Gwkhrwi kharlangni,
Jwngni ongra
Jisu Kristo-niao.

3. Jisu Kristo-anw
Iswr-ni bisajla,

phapni thakhwi,

jwng Bini onnaijwng
bwkhangjagwn.

4. Jisu Kristo-niao,

Gwia Biniao,

Gwkhrwinw

1. Jajenwiniphrai Iswr-a,

2. Obla Swr ginw, bwlwjwng

3. Buhum maniao Bini,

4. Gwjou Swrgwni sayao,

Buhuma rongjananwi,

baknaithwng.
Boibw rwjab; maonai

1. Iswr-ni bisa Jisu,

Onnaia gwbangthar.

2. Krus thongphang-ao thwinanwi,

3. Thangbai Swrgwao danw,

Swrgwao angkhou langwn,

Arw ang rwjabphlaigwn,
Onnaia gwbangthar.

1. Lwgw gwia gurwi Jisu badi;

Jisu-lo, Jisu-lo.

Gwithara, gwithara.

Sanphrwmbw, sanphrwmbw.

4. Gwthar mansiphwrkhou gargwn nama ?
Garthara, garthara.

Lathargwn, lathargwn.

Gwithara, gwithara.

mithikhagou,

3. Gwdao swrao jubra jabla,

Phwrbu-anw gwjwnhwgra,

Lwgwphra nwngkhou nagarbla,
Binaijwng Binw khwtha;
Jisu-a nwngkhounw bamgwn,

1. Swrgwni rajaya

Basaigra gwithara,
Phwrbu Jisu-alo
Jwngni borsa.

2. Angw gotho gwllwi
Badinwthar,
Gwithara angha
Phwrbu bwlwa.
Mwnbla thangoumwn ang,
Swrgw raijwaonw,
Nathai lamakhou ang
Mithithara.

3. Angni sakhathi-ao
Phwidw gotho,
Nwngswrnw lamakhou
Khwthagwn ang.
Githarnanga mungbw,
Nwngswrw phwithardw,
Lamakhou gwmadwng
Nwngswr manw ?

4. Swrgwao linghordwng
Biw jwngkhou,
Jisu-ninw onnaia
Gedertsinthar.
Buhumao swrha dong,
Bibadinw onnai ?
Angkhou lagarbw
Bi lingbai thadwng.

5. Angw nwngswrninw
Phwrbu Jisu,
Nwngswrkhou bimainw
Angw onw.
Swrgwniphrai angw,
Naihorw nwngswrkhou,
Nwngswrni gwswkhou
Swlaihwnw.

1. O basaigra Phwrbu Kristo,
Nwng-lonw angni borsa
Phwthaiyw ang.
Angniaonw thaphwidw Nwng,
Nwngni gwthar bathrajwng.

2. Phwthaiyw ang jwbajase,
Nwngni gedert onnaikhou.
Ongra Jisu,
Hephajab hw Nwngni thwijwng,
Phap'niphrai Angkhou basai.

3. Jingga sibla, gap'blabw ang,
Banjaijagwn lagarbw.
Ongra Phwrbu,
Nwngnw thabla dukhu gwia,
Nwngniaonw thagwn ang.

4. Thwndw Angkhou ongra Jisu,
Manithargwn ang Nwngkhou.
Hap'hwgwn ang gwsw-aonw,
Phwrbu-khounw,
Nwngni onnaimanijwng.

Jisu badi raobw gwia be songsarao,
Jisu badi raobw gwia.
Biw jwngkhou phapniphrainw
Bwkhangnw hagou.

1. Hayao thanai mansi mani gwglwibai,

Jisu-khou nagarnan,
jwng swrniao thangnw ?
Gwthangni bathrakhou
jwng swrniao mwnnw,
Jisu-khou nagarnan ?

1. Nwng badi lwgw O,
Jwngni ongra Jisu,
Hadort maniaonw

2. Basaibai jwngkhou Bi,
Gaoni jiu hwnaijwng,

Swrgwao hab-hwgwn.

Angw rongjatharbai,
Jisu-ni onnaikhou
Ang mwthai khonphlaigwn.

4. No' no'ao thanggwn ang,
Jeraobw khwthagwn,
Lagarbw Jisu-ni
Mungkhou ang saoraigwn.

1. Jisu Nwng gurwi, onkho,
Naihordw danw angkhou;
Nwngni khathiao thanw,
Angnwbw jaiga hwdw.

2. Angkhou Nwngniao bwlang,
Raobw dahomtharthwng;
Onnaini raijwaonw,
Jaiga hwdw angnwbw.

3. Jisu-a nisan angni,
Iswr-ni menda bisa;
Dodro, gurwi, onkhomwn,

Be hayaobw be

jwngnw nagar,
jwngbw Nwngni onnaijwng

4. Anjart lanaiaonw

Jwngkhou hompthadw,
Raijwa, bwlwa
Arw mohimaya,

Amen.

1. Angw phapi Phwrbu,

4. Nwngjwng thani Phwrbu,

1. Dagar O basaigra Angkhou,

Nwngw gubunkhou linghorbla,

Angkhou dagarlang!
O basaigra, binaikhou khwna,

4. Gwjwn hwgra dwimu Nwngw,

1. Phwrbu Jisu Nwng,

Arphojwng
Angkhou nephwidw.
Angw thangnwswi
Songsar sagwrkhou,

2. Phwrbu Jisu Nwng,
Angnw doya hw.
Angkhou phwthar
Nwngni thwijwng.
Angkhou langphwidw,
Nwngni raijwao

3. Phwrbu Jisu Nwng,
Angnw khema hw.
Angni phap'khou
Khwmwr Nwngw.

4. Apha Iswr Nwng,

5. Apha nwngniao,

Angw thangnwswi,

1. Haoriathar phapi ang,

O ongra Jisu,

2. Switankhou nagarnanwi,

3. Nwngni bwswn lanaikhai,

4. Angni jiukhou dikhang Nwng,

1. Phwrbu Jisu gwthar raja,

Siphaidw, switanni no'khou,

2. Nwng lagarbw jwngblaograthar,

3. Dersin habaphwr mania,

3. Dagi undwi phalw janji khaphra,

1. Ma esegrap' gwdwi bathra, O Phwrbu,

2. jwngni gwswphranw alangba, Phwrbu,

3. Jwngni binaiphwrkhou khwnasong, Phwrbu,

4. Jwngkhou doyajwng basaidw de, Phwrbu,

5. Jwngnw onnanwi bwlw hwdw, Phwrbu,
jwng Nwngni bwlwjwng thabaidwni.

thasandi,

1. Phapithar angw O Jisu,

5. O Jisu, Nwngni doyajwng,

1. Jwngw Jisu-ni singao,

gwjwngwn,

1. Khwmajwng khwnabai, angw

hwdw bwlwkhou.

5. Jwngni hadora khwmsithar,

6. Binikhainw jwngw boibw,

jwngni hadort, hajw, hagra,

1. Sando-ninw gejerao,

6. Dinwi Jisu doyajwng,
Nwngw jwngkhou jiraihw;

1. jwngni gedert phap'ni thakhwi,

Be badinw thwnnai

4. Nwng Iswr-ni thwnnaiphwrkhounw,

Phwrbu-ninw Deobar sankhou,

1. Jiuni dan hasthaibla,

Hwjanaini thingwi
Gwkhrwi, phwthainai

jwng lakhigwn mondolikhou,

1. Jisu-a jwngni gwgwm khunthiya,

Nwngni gwjwnnaikhou.

3. Gwjouao phap'gwia,

1. Jisu-ni Girajaya gwjam,

jwng boikhoubw gwjwnhwyw.
Jisu-a jwngni khathiao,

4. Gonthaphra jwngkhou linghorbla,

Jwngkhou Bini phwthainaiao.

1. Sabais Kristo-niao,

1. O Jwngni Iswr Apha,

3. Dinwiniphrai, O Iswr,
